    <item>
      <title>伊朗称以色列对其大院的袭击造成两名将军死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/iran-says-israeli-strike-on-embassy-compound-killed-top-general</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗和叙利亚官方媒体称，以色列对伊朗驻叙利亚大使馆大院发动空袭，造成包括一名高级军事指挥官在内的多人死亡，加剧了这两个长期对手之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/iran-says-israeli-strike-on-embassy-compound-killed-top-general</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:55:00 GMT</pubDate>
